{"tid":1806134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[解釋] Barcode 690-699 = 中國製造？","createTime":"2020-01-01T05:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T11:33:37.000Z","uid":196197,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dc0b31cfef79e551b0c775829f44c96899a792b4","tid":1806134,"uid":196197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"我哋見到有人跟據產品嘅 Barcode 首3位數字(即 GS1 Prefix) 去判斷產品係咪中國製造，如果係 690-699就係中國製造，其他就唔係。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個資料係錯的</span></strong>。跟據 GS1官方網站：<br />\n<br />\n<em>&quot;Note that since GS1 member companies can manufacture products anywhere in the world, <span style=\"color: red;\">GS1 prefixes do not identify the country of origin for a given product.</span>&quot;</em><br />\n<br />\nGS1 Prefix只係代表生產公司申請GS1 Prefix辦公室嘅地區，絕對同生產地無關架！大家唔好搞錯。<br />\n<br />\nGS1官方網站: <a href=\"https://www.gs1.org/standards/id-keys/company-prefix\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gs1.org%2Fstandards%2Fid-keys%2Fcompany-prefix&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIc3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=182e346a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gs1.org/standards/id-keys/company-prefix</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6XgMtCV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6XgMtCV.jpg&h=9fc16ec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1S0x4C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1S0x4C.jpg&h=7d58e172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3SZFx4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3SZFx4E.jpg&h=29c677f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Anywhere But China 黃色經濟戰隊<br />\n<br />\n所有已公布名單可以喺以下平台搵到<br />\nIG/FB/TG: @AnywhereButChina<br />\n<br />\n#AnywhereButChina #黃色經濟圈 #罷買中國製造</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d0b324e83eca4b33651feddb08f55409a536abe4","tid":1806134,"uid":224859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":